    "story_title": "Built for fleets that can't afford downtime",
    "story_quote": "A bus that's parked means passengers stranded. That's not acceptable.",
    "story_p1": "We started as a service workshop — repairing buses and constantly hitting the same wall: the right parts came too slow, too expensive, or simply weren't available in Moldova.",
